TextEng: You don't seem happy about that.
Text: 그것에 대해 기뻐하지 않는 것 같네요.

TextEng: You not looks happy about that.
Can I ask you a question?
Bela told me to see you.
Miss Bela say me shoulds talk to you.
And if someone were willing to help you... ?
Text: 그런데 누군가 당신을 도울 의향이 있다면...?

TextEng: And if somebody say they okays with helping you... ?
Just what do they make you do?
Can you tell me about the High Captains?
You tells me 'bout High Captains, maybe?
So you're weak, what else is new?
Text: 그러니까 당신이 약하다는 거군요. 새로운 건 없네.

TextEng: So you is weak. That not news.
Text: 그래서 너 약해. 새로운 거 아니야.

TextEng: How do I find Kurth, then?
How do I find Baram, then?
No, I don't need any key.
No, I don't need any key.
Why do you think she'd send me to you?
Text: 왜 그녀가 저를 당신한테 보냈다고 생각하죠?

TextEng: Why you thinks she sends me?
I said I thought the High Captains should be stopped.
Text: 제가 대선장들을 막아야 한다고 생각한다고 말했어요.

TextEng: Me says High Captains shoulds stop.
We were discussing the High Captains.
Miss Bela and me talks 'bout High Captains.
Why you does anything, if you not wants to?

Text: 제가 당신을 도울 수 있을지도 모르겠네요.

TextEng: Maybe you can answer some questions on the High Captains.
Text: 대선장들에 대한 질문에 답해줄 수 있을까요?

TextEng: Just what is it you do for them?
Text: 당신은 그들을 위해 정확히 뭘 하는 건가요?

TextEng: Me wants to know lots 'bout captains.
Text: 나 선장들 얘기 많이 알고 싶어.

TextEng: I want to know more about these High Captains.
Text: 이 대선장들에 대해 더 알고 싶어요.

TextEng: Why do anything for them, if you don't want to?
Text: 하기 싫으면 왜 그들을 위해 뭘 하죠?

TextEng: Me could pays you for information, if you wants.
Text: 원하면 나 정보 값으로 돈 줄 수 있어.

TextEng: You gets lots more trouble if you not answers me, get it?
Text: 대답 안 하면 더 큰 곤란해질 거야... 알겠어?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Me not tells anybody what you says.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 나 네가 한 말 아무한테도 안 말해.

TextEng: I could pay you for the information, if you like.
Text: 원하신다면 정보 값을 지불할 수 있어요.

TextEng: A surer way to trouble is not to answer my questions... get it?
Text: 제 질문에 대답하지 않는 게 더 확실한 곤란을 초래할 겁니다... 이해하시겠어요?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> I won't tell anyone what you say.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 당신이 한 말은 아무에게도 하지 않을게요.

TextEng: Who is this Rhaine you mention?
I was hoping to hire you.
You answers questions 'bout High Captains, maybe?
Can you answer some questions about the High Captains?
Text: 대선장들에 대한 질문에 답해줄 수 있어요?

TextEng: I have some questions for you.
Me think you wants to know: Kurth be dead.
Text: 나 너 알아야 한다고 생각해. 커스 죽었어.

TextEng: I thought you should know: Kurth is dead.
Text: 알아두어야 할 것 같아서요. 커스가 죽었습니다.

TextEng: Me think you wants to know: Baram be dead.
Text: 나 너 알아야 한다고 생각해. 바람 죽었어.

TextEng: I thought you should know: Baram is dead.
Text: 알아두어야 할 것 같아서요. 바람이 죽었습니다.
